body:
Hey there, thanks for making the editing experience for flutter so amazing, through this neat plugin!

---

Reporting a small inconvienience I encountered - The autocomplete feature works great, except that it completely shuts down while typing out generic arguments.



---

This 
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19492893/67633064-2b4f9580-f8d1-11e9-8211-df6d6ec47bf4.png)

vs nothing

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19492893/67633057-1a9f1f80-f8d1-11e9-9e1d-4324547a6da2.png)


---
Similiar behavor in VSCode too.

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19492893/67633003-8b920780-f8d0-11e9-950c-2b10579956c3.png)
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19492893/67633028-d27ffd00-f8d0-11e9-9e55-9d0d4441e718.png)
